    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014very well-loved and runs like a dream! This car is perfect for someone looking for a dependable, comfortable vehicle that\u2019s been treated with a lot of care. I\u2019ve kept up with all the maintenance, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next adventure. I'd love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit delivers linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained for performance, including essential subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to preserve its legendary handling dynamics. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing exceptional feedback through the steering rack. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is dialed in and ready for immediate spirited use. A true driver's specimen with all major mechanical services up to date.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean title. Reliable daily driver. Minor cosmetic wear only.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Available now is a beautifully maintained 2019 Lexus RX 350 finished in a deep Obsidian Black. This vehicle has been driven with care and serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection will reveal some light road-wear and minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Parchment leather; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, with only slight softening on the driver-side bolster. It has been a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine performs flawlessly, offering the smooth, quiet power Lexus is known for. The transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. All premium features, including the heated and ventilated seats, navigation system, and power liftgate, are in perfect working order. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes were recently inspected and cleared for many more miles. This is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking luxury and peace of mind without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been maintained to a high standard of excellence. It offers a seamless blend of performance and reliability, ensuring a superior driving experience for its next owner. This acquisition represents a sound investment in both quality and prestige.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car. It's been a super reliable ride and is still in really solid shape! It runs beautifully and has been well-loved, so it's perfect if you're looking for something dependable and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love driving it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
